Plugin ameletHDFReader
======================

AmeletHDFReader is a plugin for the 3D tool ParaView (http://www.paraview.org/).

This plugin allow to the user the import of AmeletHDF files in ParaView. These files
are :

* Structured Meshes.
* Unstructured meshes.
* Data.
* Data on mesh.

To build plugin ameletHDFReader, please follow these instructions:

1) Install package paraview-dev
2) Build and Install the library amelethdf-c (https://git.framasoft.org/axessim/amelethdf-c)
3) Create a build directory and use cmake tool in order to build the plugin


PS : The hdf library version should be 1.8.x


